, wave your hand!\"'),(272,'Waiting Room','🏆 Colors and clothing challenge','Go back and forth between colors you are wearing and colors your child is wearing to help them learn the game.'),(273,'Waiting Room','Clock in some clock time','Find a clock and say, \"Look there is a clock! It is a circle. It has two hands that go around and around the clock.\"'),(274,'Waiting Room','Clock in some clock time','Watch the clock as it moves around.'),(275,'Waiting Room','Clock in some clock time','Tell your child, \"Let\'s move our hands around and around like the clock!\"'),(276,'Waiting Room','Clock in some clock time','Show your child a hand gesture. Imitate 🔄 and enjoy what your child does.'),(277,'Waiting Room','🏆 Silly faces challenge: See how many times you can get your child to laugh.','Share ideas for silly faces. \"We can make monster faces!\" \"We can make fish faces.\" If your child laughs, say, \"You thinks that\'s a funny face!\" or \"Funny faces are so silly.\"'),(278,'Waiting Room','🏆 Silly faces challenge: See how many times you can get your child to laugh.','Take turns making funny faces and imitating each other.'),(279,'Waiting Room','Have fun with emotions','Talk to your child about emotions.'),(280,'Waiting Room','Have fun with emotions','Label 💁 your child\'s face, \"I see you smiling, you must be happy!\" Imitate 🔄 your child\'s face.'),(281,'Waiting Room','Have fun with emotions','Show your child an angry face, and say \"Let me see your angry face!\" Enjoy your child\'s face, and imitate what they do.'),(282,'Waiting Room','Waiting Room 101: Waiting & Listening','Waiting is hard for everyone! Help your child by preparing them. Say, \"First, we sit here and listen for our name! Then we go back to a room.\"'),(283,'Waiting Room','Waiting Room 101: Waiting & Listening','When a name is called say, \"Was that our name?\" Repeat 🔄  back your child\'s response.'),(284,'Waiting Room','Waiting Room 101: Waiting & Listening','If your child doesn\'t answer by talking or gestures say, \"No, that wasn\'t our name. Let\'s keep listening!\"'),(285,'Waiting Room','Let\'s look for the color blue today','Tell your child, \"Let\'s find the color blue! Help your child by finding one blue thing, and say, \"The pen is blue!\" Ask your child, \"What color is this?\"'),(286,'Waiting Room','Let\'s look for the color blue today','Repeat back the response, or if there isn\'t one, you can label the color.'),(287,'Waiting Room','Let\'s look for the color blue today','Look around the room and label 💁three more blue items in the room.'),(288,'Waiting Room','Talk about if the room is quiet or loud','Ask your child to listen, and say, \"It is very quiet in here! I\'m going to use my whisper voice!\" Talk to your child in a whisper.'),(289,'Waiting Room','Talk about if the room is quiet or loud','Try using different levels of whispering with silly faces to keep your child excited.'),(290,'Waiting Room','Talk about if the room is quiet or loud','Tell your child, \"Let me hear you whisper!\" Imitate 🔄 the sounds or whispering words your child makes.'),(291,'Waiting Room','Give positive attention👏 to help while waiting!','Waiting is hard for everyone! Giving positive attention 👏 can help your child as they wait. When your child is being patient say, \"You are being so patient while we wait!\"'),(292,'Waiting Room','Give positive attention👏 to help while waiting!','When fitting, you can also say, \"You have a calm body, that helps us wait!\"'),(293,'Waiting Room','Give positive attention👏 to help while waiting!','Look for other times you are proud of your child, and label 💁these moments!'),(294,'Waiting Room','Find an old picture on your phone and tell a story  💁 about it','Show your child the picture and comment or label 💁 about what you are doing in the picture, or make a story for the picture.'),(295,'Waiting Room','Find an old picture on your phone and tell a story  💁 about it','Ask your child or baby, \"Where\'s [your child\'s name]?\" Watch for your child to point, look, or gesture at the picture.'),(296,'Waiting Room','Find an old picture on your phone and tell a story  💁 about it','Repeat 🔄 back your child\'s gesture and expand by saying, \"Yes, this is you! Your name is...\"'),(297,'Waiting Room','Help your child wait by singing their favorite song','Singing songs is a great way to interact and talk with your child.'),(298,'Waiting Room','Help your child wait by singing their favorite song','Help your child learn the words by singing the song with your child. Before singing the next word wait 5 seconds ⏳ to let your child fill in the blank.'),(299,'Waiting Room','Help your child wait by singing their favorite song','Sing the word for your child after 5 seconds for your child to hear. Babies may sing with babbles and gestures!'),(300,'Waiting Room','Let\'s play simon says!','Simon Says with Babies: Help your child'),(301,'Waiting Room','👀 See what your child sees','Play a game where you guess what your child is looking at.'),(302,'Waiting Room','👀 See what your child sees','Watch to see where your child is looking and take a guess: \"I think you\'re looking at...\"'),(303,'Waiting Room','👀 See what your child sees','Give your child the chance to nod \"yes\" or \"no.\"'),(304,'Other\'s Home','Help your child say hi with choices','First, model for your child by saying hello to others.'),(305,'Other\'s Home','Help your child say hi with choices','Watch to see if your child is feeling shy. If so, you can give a choice like, \"Do you want to wave or give a high five?\" to help your child feel more comfortable'),(306,'Other\'s Home','Help your child say hi with choices','If your child doesn\'t respond, model again: \"Hello! How are you?\"'),(307,'Other\'s Home','Social Butterfly Detector','Watch for moments when your child is showing great social behaviors. Examples could be smiling at others, babbling, sharing, or using good manners.'),(308,'Other\'s Home','Social Butterfly Detector','Tell your child what you like about how they are being social: \"You are sharing nicely.\" \"You gave ___ a nice smile!\"'),(309,'Other\'s Home','Social Butterfly Detector','Use the tone of your voice to show your child how proud you are.'),(310,'Other\'s Home','Let your child find the best spot in the house!','Ask your child, \"where should we go to play?\"'),(311,'Other\'s Home','Let your child find the best spot in the house!','Watch to see where your child looks, gestures, or points to.'),(312,'Other\'s Home','Let your child find the best spot in the house!','If your child doesn\'t respond in 5 seconds, help your child make a choice, \"Should we go to the couch or sit on the rug?\"'),(313,'Other\'s Home','Let your child find the best spot in the house!','By observing what your child is interested in you can help them make a choice.');
